			<h2><a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=47" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to We love Ashton Court">We love Ashton Court</a></h2>
			<h4>April 25th, 2007<!-- by Clare --> &middot; <a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=47#comments" title="Comment on We love Ashton Court">1 Comment</a></h4>
			<div class="entry">
				<p>Festivals are expensive. 2006&#8217;s event cost over £650,000. In addition, extras including new regulations, graffiti and other clear up &#8216;issues&#8217; totalled £100,000. For Ashton Court festival to remain in operation it needs help - cue the new &#8216;<a href="http://www.weloveashtoncourtfestival.com/" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.weloveashtoncourtfestival.com/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=6');">We Love Ashton Court&#8217;</a> website. Visit <a href="http://www.weloveashtoncourtfestival.com/" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.weloveashtoncourtfestival.com/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=6');">now</a> to find out how you can get involved.</p>
